# $extension_name

An [Agent Forge](https://github.com/akoita/agent-forge) extension.

## Installation

```bash
pip install agent-forge-$extension_name
```

Or for development:

```bash
pip install -e .
```

## Usage

Once installed, the extension is automatically discovered by Agent Forge:

```bash
# List installed extensions
agent-forge extensions list

# Use the default profile
agent-forge run --profile $package_name-default --task "Your task" --repo ./your-repo
```

To build a hosted-service image with this extension installed:

```bash
docker build \
  --build-arg AGENT_FORGE_IMAGE=agent-forge-service:latest \
  -t agent-forge-$extension_name:latest .
```

## Development

```bash
# Install in development mode with test dependencies
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Run tests
pytest
```

## Project Structure

```
$extension_name/
├── Dockerfile
├── pyproject.toml
├── README.md
├── $package_name/
│   ├── __init__.py           # Extension metadata
│   ├── profiles/
│   │   └── default.yaml      # Agent profiles
│   └── tools/
│       └── sample_tool.py    # Custom tools
└── tests/
    └── test_sample_tool.py
```
